wiki.summary: Split album (Dark Funeral / Infernal) - Released on May 25th, 2002 by Hammerheart Records Contains Dark Funeral's "Dark Funeral" EP and Infernal's "Infernal" EP. Dark Funeral claims this release is a bootleg, while the label says otherwise. Dark Funeral: 1. Open the Gates 2. Shadows Over Transylvania 3. My Dark Desires 4. In the Sign of the Horns Infernal: 5. Requiem (The Coming Age of Satan) 6. Wrath of the Infernal One 7. Storms of Armageddon Read more on Last.fm.
wiki.content: Split album (Dark Funeral / Infernal) - Released on May 25th, 2002 by Hammerheart Records Contains Dark Funeral's "Dark Funeral" EP and Infernal's "Infernal" EP. Dark Funeral claims this release is a bootleg, while the label says otherwise. Dark Funeral: 1. Open the Gates 2. Shadows Over Transylvania 3. My Dark Desires 4. In the Sign of the Horns Infernal: 5. Requiem (The Coming Age of Satan) 6. Wrath of the Infernal One 7. Storms of Armageddon 8. Under the Hellsign Tracks 1 to 4 recorded & mixed at Hellspawn/Unisound Studios, January 1994. Tracks 5 to 8 recorded at Dugout Studio, August 1998. Completed in 1999 at the Abyss. Read more on Last.fm.
